        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "All the tribes of Israel—the Lord’s people— make their pilgrimage here. They come to give thanks to the name of the Lord, as the law requires of Israel. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
